@jongyoul 
When using provided and bringing in all hadoop dependencies to zengine by adding hadoop lib in HADOOP_CONF_DIR to the classpath, Zeppelin raise an exception at runtime.

However by bringing explicitely in scope to the zengine only hadoop-hdfs and hadoop-common, everything works as intended.

